"-//NLM//DTD BITS Structural Table of Contents Module v1.0 20131225//EN" 
"BITS-toc1.ent"                                                      >



<!--                    BITS STRUCTURAL NAVIGATION MODULE          --><!--                    Element declarations for BITS navigation
                        and pointing mechanism for structural
